name: Jesus in Her Mouth
description:
This is Jo, a super creative and beautiful Italian model I shot in Berlin!  Her Ouija board tattoo inspired this sinister look,  so we dressed her in this hot goth outfit and horns.  I love all the spooky art she has tattooed on her skin.  We used a slow exposure and draped some LED lights to get the light trails.  I love experimenting with simple but dramatic lighting effects. Jo is licking a rosary, I guess she has a little bit of a dark side.....
